::KitKat::

She jumped back at the image of the fire. "GROWL!"
She snapped her teeth and growled.

she stopped for a moment and walked over to Stringtra, "If she wasn't 
trying to help him, I'd tear her apart.  I don't like her a bit.  She 
wolf fodder as far as I'm concerned."

She walked out of the room and into the main room.  She noticed that 
the room was unoccupied.  She sniffed around. No scents out of the 
ordinary, she thought. "Must be out on a huntof a good fight."  She 
turned and went to a corner of the cave.  She curled up and kept 
watch.
